name: autocuidado
description:
selfcare is important, don't forget to water yourself

This piece is from the collection "descartável", which is a audiovisual project that I discarded bad feelings and turned it into something that could heal me. The project addresses mental health issues, self knowledge and it was a opportunity to me to study animation. This is the 15th piece of the collection.
